abstract: Caroline Kennedy, whose endorsement of Barack Obama in 2008 was a setback for Hillary Rodham Clinton's campaign, as well as personal blow, says she will 'absolutely' support Clinton should she decide to run for president again.
lead_paragraph: Ms. Kennedy, whose endorsement of Barack Obama in 2008 was a setback for Hillary Rodham Clinton, said she would “absolutely” support Mrs. Clinton should she decide to run for president again.

headline.main: Caroline Kennedy Says She Will Back Hillary Clinton in a Run for President
